Interface CanvasExporter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CanvasToSVGExporter, CanvasToWebExporter

    public interface CanvasExporter
    A Canvas exporter converts a canvas object into output file. For example, you can convert a canvas into a SVG image.
